If you have any problems, please contact us at support@marmitek.com.

Smart me offers the most comprehensive voice-controlled smart home experience with Alexa.
Control your home lighting and other devices hands free. Just say it, Smart me will obey.

Here's a step by step guide:
(1). Download our "Smart me" app in Google Play or iOS Store;
(2). Launch the app and register a new account (or login if you're already registered);
(3). Turn your Smart me devices on and connect them with the "Smart me" app;
(4). IMPORTANT: You can rename the devices with the Smart me app. So if you rename a smart bulb "Livingroom Light", then the device in Amazon Echo will get that same name after the device is added in Step 9;
(5). Download the Amazon "Alexa" app from the Amazon market, Google Play or iOS App Store, and connect the Echo with the "Alexa" app;
(6). Search the Alexa Skills directory for "Smart me";
(7). When the skill is found, you Click on "ENABLE TO USE", then input your "Smart me" account username, password and region on the linking page;
(8). Then say "Alexa, discover devices." to the Echo. Wait till the Echo says "Discover is completed";
(9). Now your setup is done. Try to talk to the Echo to control your devices.

Here are the voice commands Smart me has:

Light

Alexa, turn on the lighting
Alexa, dim the lights
Alexa, set the light to blue

SMARTPLUG

Alexa, turn on the smart plug
Alexa, turn off the smart plug

SWITCH

Alexa, turn on the switch
Alexa, turn off the switch
